aygan (s tegrigit taqburt : Αιγάν) d aɣella abizenṭi yeddren deg lɛehd n Justinyan 

== tudert ==
yettwabder-d deg yunyu 530 , deg tnegluft n Dara mi yella ɣer tama n yirumaniyen mgal ifarsiyen 

deg 533 yettwaceyyeɛ ɣer tefriqt n ugafa akked yiɣella nniḍen ( gar-asen [[Rufan]] ) akken ad nnaɣen mgal [[Jelimar]] awendali . deg unebdu n 534 yeggra-d netta d Rufan s ddaw n tmehla n [[Sliman]] , deg taggara n useggas-nni ruḥen ad nnaɣen d kra n yiderman n yimaziɣen i sen yuwin iserdasen , maca zzin-asen ; yettwanɣa Aygan
